 = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = =   Hi Frank & All, My question is: How does Chris Moon KNOW we all are getting &quot;False communications&quot; from &quot;dark entities&quot; or whatever he is claiming???! This is an insult (slap-in-the-face comment) and untrue = thus &quot;slander&quot;! IMHO I personally don&#39;t like it! I have been researching EVP&#39;s - on & off - since about 1968-1970, when I first heard about it! Longer than Chris has been alive! 8-(     =Judy=
